  "1798720": {
    "name": "诺拉的魔药日记",
    "steam_appid": 1798720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "这是一款十分休闲的模拟经营游戏，你将化身为魔药师诺拉，成为本世纪最伟大的魔药师！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种植属于自己的魔药园</h2>你拥有一处特殊的魔药园，在这里你可以种植多种魔药，精心呵护这些魔药，并采摘你所需要的魔药原材料。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/4cef01041ec7e00a77f5706c6b8936d0.poster.avif?t=1757700785\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/4cef01041ec7e00a77f5706c6b8936d0.webm?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/4cef01041ec7e00a77f5706c6b8936d0.mp4?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >炼制具有神秘力量的魔药  </h2>通过你收集的原材料进行不同的组合，从而炼制效果不一的魔药，伴随着你的魔药经验越发成熟，你可以炼制超过五十种不同的魔药。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/1613e1cf08fa9af48fa2bb115a023801.poster.avif?t=1757700785\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/1613e1cf08fa9af48fa2bb115a023801.webm?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/1613e1cf08fa9af48fa2bb115a023801.mp4?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >贩卖魔药赚取更多的金币</h2>你所炼制的任何魔药都可以出售，通过贩卖魔药获得的金币，你可以购买更多的原材料或者家具。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/7caea29ef32786763e96ac5d20ef2237.poster.avif?t=1757700785\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/7caea29ef32786763e96ac5d20ef2237.webm?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/7caea29ef32786763e96ac5d20ef2237.mp4?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >购买心仪家具装扮房间</h2>通过出售魔药赚取金币，从而购买家精心打扮自己的房间，多种样式多种款式的家具任你挑选。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/bfa6d269d4de607bec46ccfdfc3e3f18.poster.avif?t=1757700785\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/bfa6d269d4de607bec46ccfdfc3e3f18.webm?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/bfa6d269d4de607bec46ccfdfc3e3f18.mp4?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当然，收拾房间同样也是重中之重，清扫灰尘驱逐害虫也是需要小女巫亲力亲为的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/f398889ea25a3ef2e75c478f391f17a6.poster.avif?t=1757700785\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/f398889ea25a3ef2e75c478f391f17a6.webm?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798720/extras/f398889ea25a3ef2e75c478f391f17a6.mp4?t=1757700785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
